sub_title: Owner/founder Gabber music Label ''Hardcore From Hell''
summary:
Pieter Lep aka Dj dr. Oldschool    Gabber since 1990

allias:

Dr. Lep
Dr. Melody
Dr. invincible
The Oldschoolman

Style: Gabberhouse, Early rave, Early hardcore

In the past i was resident dj in a spot in Leeuwarden and played as dj on small party's.

i still make mixes and place them on social sites as Facebook, Youtube, and on special artists sites as Myspace, Internet dj or Sectionz for example. 

on this type of site's you can place your own made dj gigs and productions.

I only mix with turntables and record my gigs with a special computer program. in the past i used Fruity loops for making my own production's

for dj bookings you can send a mail to (pieterlep@gmail.com)

check this link for my latest online mix, you can also download it

http://www.sectionz.com/detail.asp?rType=mp3&SZID=32725

Specialties: i can give you some gabber lessons.

profile_positions.description:
Hardcore from hell is a small gabberhouse label. in the past i made music productions on cd's under the name Hardcore from hell, i spread the cd's under friends and mate's.

I made also mix tape's under the name Hardcore from hell and spread them. productions i don't make anymore at the end i don't have the patience to make numbers.

this label is now defunct.
